Subject: [PATCHSET] PC-9800 subarch. support for 2.5.61 (4/26) boot
Message-ID: <20030217135448.GD4799@yuzuki.cinet.co.jp>
References: <20030217134333.GA4734@yuzuki.cinet.co.jp>
